# XAI Trust, Governance & Certification Framework — Implementation Plan

## Overview
Build a compliance-grade XAI governance layer for RBI's half-yearly publications (FSR, MPR, PSR, FER) using **Python/FastAPI** backend + **React** frontend, powered by **Gemini Pro 3.0**.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[React Frontend] --> B[FastAPI Gateway]
    B --> C[Ingestion Service - BP1]
    B --> D[RAG + Hallucination Engine - BP2]
    B --> E[BRD Compliance Engine - BP3]
    C --> F[(ChromaDB Vector Store)]
    C --> G[(SQLite Metadata DB)]
    D --> F
    D --> H[Gemini Pro 3.0]
    E --> F
    E --> H
```

